	(11, 'Chew Wai Sim', '+60 16-332 0676', 'leodineinthedark@gmail.com', 'Leo Club of Taylor\'s University Lakeside Campus', 'I’m Jantzen User', 'WellnessWave: Walk, Screen, Shop!', 'Fundraising and Walkathon', '2024-03-03', '2024-03-03', 'Subang Parade, Jalan Kemajuan Subang, SS 16, 47500 Subang Jaya, Selangor', 'Approx. 400 people', 'Complimentary items for attendees (e.g., in gift bags or as souvenirs)', 'Yes', '“WellnessWave: Walk, Screen, Shop!” is a charitable initiative organised by the six Leo Clubs and Lions Club of Subang Jaya. Leo Club is a youth organization under the Lions Clubs International that encourages young individuals to serve others for the betterment of their communities and the world. Leos worldwide share a collective dedication to making a positive and lasting impact, driven by a passion to help those in need.\r\n\r\nSponsoring our event aimed at raising funds for the National Kidney Foundation of Malaysia (NKF) plays a crucial role in the fight against diabetes and various kidney diseases. According to NKF, more than one million people in Malaysia have diabetes and it also contributes to 57% of kidney failure. Besides, this event also aims to encourage individuals to be physically active as a means of improving health and to raise awareness about the importance of regular health check-ups for early detection of health issues. By partnering with us, your organisation not only aligns with a noble cause but also actively contributes to initiatives that positively impact the lives of countless individuals affected by these diseases.\r\n\r\nThe main components of the event include a 5-kilometre walkathon and complimentary health screening. To enhance the experience, a bazaar with over 20 vendors will be featured on the event day. 90% of the profits earned from this event will be donated to the NKF to help sustain the organisation. \r\n\r\nWe are anticipating 350+ participants to join us for the event. We appreciate sponsorships of all forms, from 