	(57, 'Nur Fathihah binti Shipul Bahri', '(+60)173460917', 'mktbsekrum@gmail.com', 'Sekretariat Sukarelawan Universiti Malaya (SEKRUM)', 'Events', 'Misi Kemanusian Tempatan Borneo', 'Community, Engagement, Education', '2024-07-10', '2024-07-21', 'Kampung Gallam Gallam, Semporna, Sabah', '50', 'Complimentary items for attendees (e.g., in gift bags or as souvenirs)', 'No', 'Embarking on a mission to foster holistic development and enduring impact in education and community development for the residents of Borneo is our overarching commitment. At the core of our strategy is the cultivation of robust relationships with the Borneo community, providing Universiti Malaya students with an active platform for volunteer engagement.\r\n\r\nThe chosen focal point for our mission is the state of Sabah, where a pervasive lack of awareness within the community regarding critical issues in education, health, and technology, particularly in rural areas, requires our attention.\r\n\r\nThe involvement of 25 volunteers in this mission serves as a transformative catalyst, enhancing their interpersonal skills and concurrently positioning Universiti Malaya and our esteemed sponsors as trailblazers in the expansive realm of volunteer programs throughout Malaysia.\r\n\r\nOur commitment extends beyond mere external impact; we recognize the imperative of direct involvement with community members. Through our mission, we aim to illuminate the intrinsic significance of community development, specifically within the realm of education. The anticipated enduring benefits are poised to empower community members, enabling them to contribute meaningfully to their respective communities and fostering sustainable growth and improvement.', '["uploads/SURAT KEBENARAN MENGUTIP TAJAAN.pdf1705757024.pdf", "uploads/MKTB PROPOSAL - VERSI BAHASA MELAYU.pdf1705757024.pdf"]', '5', '0', NULL, '0', '12', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NUL