	(58, 'Nurmyrzatul Athirah Abd Jalil', '01137797984', 'upmkmbk@gmail.com', 'Kelab Mahasiswa Bimbingan dan Kaunseling Universiti Putra Malaysia (UPM)', 'Friends/Family', 'Program Operasi Khidmat Masyarakat (OPKIM)', 'Community', '2024-02-16', '2024-02-18', 'Felda Lepang Nenering, Pengkalan Hulu, Perak', '200', 'Complimentary items for attendees (e.g., in gift bags or as souvenirs)', 'No', 'Operasi Khidmat Masyarakat (OPKIM), organized by the Student Guidance and Counseling Club (KMBK), is a 3-day, 2-night program in the form of community service for UPM\'s counseling students. This community service program is organized to provide an opportunity for counseling students to experience the culture and lifestyle of the community apart from their own community. The Program Operasi Khidmat Masyarakat (OPKIM) is also carried out with the concept of "Anak Angkat" with the aim of making students aware of the social responsibility they play in providing service to the community as well as being able to hone their communication skills with the outside community more effectively. Students can cultivate a sense of concern for themselves as they go hand in hand with being able to strengthen the relationship between students and the outside community. For this 3-day, 2-night program, some of the main activities that will be conducted include the village\'s tradition, which is "Rewang" as well as the "Malam Budaya" which will include all of the families that take part in this program. There will also be a special slot in which the local community there will take charge of showing the students their local\'s specialties in earning money through agricultural activities that coincides with the history of the establishment of UPM as an agricultural university. The local community as well as the UPM entity will be seeing how this kind of community service program is one of the many great ways to increase students\' knowledge about the customs and culture of the locals.', '["uploads/15-1-2024 - Kertas Kerja OPKIM KMBK 23_24.pdf1705832512.pdf"]', '5', '9', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Approved', 'NotFilled', NULL, '9ctn of 500ml', NULL, 'Naomis', '[""]', NULL, '2024-01-21 02:21:56', '2024-01-21 17:18:47', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', NULL, NULL),
