	(98, 'Tee Wan Yong', '+60-174218687', 'carebearsultimate@gmail.com', 'Carebears Ultimate Flying Disc Club', 'Social Media', 'Sports Team Sponsorship', 'Sports Team Sponsorship', '2024-04-01', '2024-12-31', 'Petaling Jaya', '700~800', 'Others', 'Yes', 'Opportunity for to tap into a new sports market.\r\n\r\nDear Jantzen team,\r\n\r\nI hope this message finds you well. I am reaching out to discuss an exciting opportunity for Jantzen to become a sponsor of our esteemed Carebears Ultimate Flying Disc Club. Carebears Ultimate is a dedicated and passionate group of athletes who have consistently demonstrated excellence both on and off the field/court. Our team has been making waves in the local and international scene. We believe that partnering with Jantzen would not only benefit our team but also provide your company with valuable exposure and brand visibility.\r\n\r\nHere are some key benefits of sponsoring:\r\n1.	Targeted Marketing: Tournaments often cater to specific demographics, such as sports enthusiasts or gamers. This allows you to target your marketing efforts towards a relevant audience, increasing the chances of converting attendees into customers.\r\n2.	Brand Visibility: Tournaments attract large crowds, providing significant exposure for your brand. Having your brand\'s logo displayed on water bottles, banners, or sponsor boards can increase brand awareness.\r\n3.	Health and Wellness Connection: Positioning your brand as a provider of clean, refreshing water aligns with the growing consumer interest in health and wellness. Emphasizing the benefits of staying hydrated during physical activities can further enhance your brand\'s appeal.\r\n4.	Community Engagement: By sponsoring our team, your company will demonstrate its commitment to supporting local athletics and fostering community engagement, which can enhance your brand\'s reputation and goodwill.\r\n5.	Sampling Opportunities: If you are keen to sample your products at event tournaments, our Carebears Ultimate sponsorship team are open to represent your brand to work on a campaign during tournament events. By providing your branded water at tournaments, you can showcase your product directly to potential customers. If attendees enjoy your water during the event, they may be more likely to purchase it in the future.\r\n6.	Online Engagement: Utilize Carebears Ultimate social media and online platforms to engage with tournament attendees before, during, and after the event. We can create branded hashtags, run contests, or share user-generated content to generate buzz and foster a sense of community around your brand.\r\n\r\nOverall, participating in tournaments can provide a valuable platform for promoting your drinking water brand, reaching new customers, and increasing brand loyalty.\r\n\r\nWe understand that every sponsorship is unique, and we are open to discussing customized sponsorship packages that align with your company\'s marketing objectives and budget. Whether you are interested in a title sponsorship, advertising opportunities, or brand visibility initiatives, we are committed to creating a mutually beneficial partnership.\r\n\r\nPlease let us know if you would be interested in exploring this opportunity further or if you have any questions. We would be more than happy to arrange a meeting to discuss potential sponsorship options in more detail.\r\n\r\nThank you for considering this partnership opportunity. We look forward to the possibility of working together to achieve our mutual goals.\r\n\r\nWarm regards,\r\nTee Wan Yong\r\nSponsorship Manager\r\nCarebears Ultimate Flying Disc Club\r\n+60-17-4218687', '["uploads/Carebears Sponsorship Deck 2024 - Jantzen.pdf1706954846.pdf"]', '0', '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Approved', 'NotFilled', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Umi', '[""]', NULL, '2024-02-03 02:07:31', '2024-02-04 23:30:59', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL,