ontact me at +60 18-763 9123 or zoelh2301@gmail.com. We are more than happy to provide a detailed sponsorship proposal and answer any questions you may have.\r\n \r\nThank you for considering our request. We believe that together, we can make a meaningful impact on the safety and well-being of our community.\r\n                                                                                                 \r\nWe look forward to the possibility of partnering with Jantzen Water (Mineral Water & Water Delivery) - HQ Puchong Branch for this important event.\r\n \r\nSincerely,\r\n \r\nZoe Lee Ling Hui\r\nExternal Liaison\r\n"Your Quick Response, Their Second Chance"\r\nSCOME SMMAMS\r\n+60 18-763 9123', '["uploads/SMMAMS First Aid Workshop .pdf1707142808.pdf"]', '0', '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Approved', 'NotFilled', NULL, 'check on sponsor in return & water qty', NULL, 'Naomis', '[""]', NULL, '2024-02-05 06:20:12', '2024-02-13 19:07:41', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', NULL, NULL),
