	(121, 'MUHAMMAD  \'AMMAAR FIRDAUS BIN AZMAN', '0183811630', '214223@student.upm.edu.my', 'MAJLIS PERWAKILAN FAKULTI BIOTEKNOLOGI DAN SAINS BIOMOLEKUL (BIOMIX)', 'Events', 'BIO FUN RUN', '5 KM MARATHON', '2024-04-28', '2024-04-28', 'Panggung Percubaan, Pusat Kebudayaan & Kesenian Sultan Salahuddin Abdul Aziz Shah,Persiaran Tulang Daing, 43400 Serdang, Selangor', 'Approximately 250 peoples', 'Complimentary items for attendees (e.g., in gift bags or as souvenirs)', 'Yes', 'Bio Fun Run is a running program organized by the Faculty of Biotechnology and Biomolecular Science Representative Council (BioMIX), in collaboration with the Universiti Putra Malaysia Student Union and the Student Affairs Division of Universiti Putra Malaysia.  The main goal of this program is to improve the level of physical and mental health, in addition to promoting healthy lifestyle practices among the citizens of Universiti Putra Malaysia.\r\n\r\n\r\nAlong with the name of this program \'Bio Fun Run\', this running event also maintains the identity of the Faculty of Biotechnology and Biomolecular Science while promoting it throughout Universiti Putra Malaysia with the theme of Biotechnology. The main activity for Bio Fun Run is the 5KM marathon around Universiti Putra Malaysia. The application for 350mL Jantzen Mineral Water is for all the participants that were exhausted from the marathon. This activity will start early, 7.30am with the coming of all participants, followed at 8.00am we will have the opening ceremony. Flag off will begin at 9.00am and will end at 11.00am. Then, from 11.00am until 12.00 we will have a prize-giving ceremony. And at 12.00pm we will have a special performance by an invited artist. And finally, the event will be end at 1.00pm. From the activities carried out, students can release all pressure while also being able to train themselves to always be in an active state.  Thus, to some extent, it can help improve their academic performance, because a fit body will produce a smart mind.  All the experience and skills gained can be used in the future.  This is because students are an important asset and lawyer in leading the country\'s government in the future.', '[]', '0', '0', NULL, '0', '10', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Processing', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-02-08 00:37:11', '2024-02-13 19:00:32', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-02-13 19:00:32', 'none', NULL, NULL),
